body language. I've got this book on it.

266
00:25:28,209 --> 00:25:30,099
Body language? I thought you
were limping.

267
00:25:30,332 --> 00:25:31,808
I was 'talking' to them!

268
00:25:32,185 --> 00:25:34,774
