Corniche obstructing your three-wheeled van.

283
00:27:07,869 --> 00:27:08,416
Why?

284
00:27:09,206 --> 00:27:14,395
Because he'll announce over the mike 'Would the owner of
the brand-new Rolls Royce Corniche kindly move it

285
00:27:14,695 --> 00:27:24,870
