00:29:01,669 --> 00:29:05,728
and knocked out two gross of
fire salvaged Rubik cubes in Croydon shopping precinct.

306
00:29:06,053 --> 00:29:08,375
Tantalize 'em Rodney,
tantalize 'em.

307
00:29:09,496 --> 00:29:10,510
